      <title>个人网站部署，基于（hexo+Github）</title>
      <link href="/2022/08/01/%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%EF%BC%88hexo+Github%EF%BC%89/"/>
      <url>/2022/08/01/%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%EF%BC%88hexo+Github%EF%BC%89/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="个人网站部署，基于（hexo-Github）"><a href="#个人网站部署，基于（hexo-Github）" class="headerlink" title="个人网站部署，基于（hexo+Github）"></a>个人网站部署，基于（hexo+Github）</h1><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>作为一个小白，一直想要一个自己的博客平台，之前是使用的wordpress基本只要设置好了环境就是一键部署，网站依赖于服务器，</p><p>但是自己想了一下不仅仅是需要一个博客而来创造博客，搭建的过程也是一个学习的过程，大概了解前端的知识，而且hexo可以把网站托管到github上这样就算服务器到期了也可以继续使用，所以这样就开始了我敲代码建站之旅。</p><p>所有处理方式基于Mac，win可以此类推 </p><p>文件位置：/Users/yourname/Documents/blog</p><h2 id="前期准备"><a href="#前期准备" class="headerlink" title="前期准备"></a>前期准备</h2><h3 id="编辑使用工具"><a href="#编辑使用工具" class="headerlink" title="编辑使用工具"></a>编辑使用工具</h3><p>markdown</p><p>Webstrom</p><h3 id="搭建工具"><a href="#搭建工具" class="headerlink" title="搭建工具"></a>搭建工具</h3><p>环境搭建：git</p><p>版本控制工具：node.js</p><p>javaScript运行环境：npm、cnmp、yarn</p><p>npm (node package manager)是 JavaScript 世界的包管理工具,并且是 Node.js 平台的默认包管理工具</p><p>获取root权限</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">sudo</span> <span class="string">sh</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id="hexo博客搭建"><a href="#hexo博客搭建" class="headerlink" title="hexo博客搭建"></a>hexo博客搭建</h2><p>安装hexo</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">npm</span> <span class="string">install</span> <span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">-g</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>确认hexo 版本</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>确认所有插件版本</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">git</span> <span class="string">version</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">node</span> <span class="string">-v</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">npm</span> <span class="string">-v</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">-v</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#查看当前所在目录路径</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">Pwd</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#查看当前目录下文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">ls</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#切换至目标文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">cd</span> <span class="string">指定文件夹</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>安装hexo文件到Documents中的指定文件夹blog</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#方法一：</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">init</span> <span class="string">blog</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#方法二</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">mkdir</span> <span class="string">blog</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="comment">#生成hexo基础框架内容(mac加 sudo以管理员的身份运行)</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">sudo</span> <span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">init</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>查看目录</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">ls</span> <span class="string">-l</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hwangkiki/picohub/img/%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2022-08-01%2014.01.03.png" alt="截屏2022-08-01 14.01.03"></p><p>输入依赖</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">npm</span> <span class="string">install</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hwangkiki/picohub/img/%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2022-08-01%2014.03.40.png" alt="截屏2022-08-01 14.03.40"></p><p>基础布置ok了</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hwangkiki/picohub/img/%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2022-08-01%2014.05.30.png" alt="截屏2022-08-01 14.05.30"></p><p>博客预览</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">s</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><img src="http://rg0quhtiy.hn-bkt.clouddn.com/hexoimg/202208041141769.png" alt="hexo"></p><p>  本地预览：<a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000/</a></p><p>tips：</p><p>安装的时候一定得切换到对应目录下操作</p><p>可能会出现出现像这样4000端口被占用的情况,可以i查看一下4000端口，没有什么用的话，就kiil掉。</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">netstat</span> <span class="string">-ant</span> <span class="string">|grep</span> <span class="number">4000</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>或者可以直接修改端口运行</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">server</span> <span class="string">-p</span> <span class="number">4018</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id="网站部署上传代码到Github"><a href="#网站部署上传代码到Github" class="headerlink" title="网站部署上传代码到Github"></a>网站部署上传代码到Github</h2><blockquote><p>1 网站注册（最好使用google账号）</p><p>2 仓库建立</p><p>3.配置git</p></blockquote><h3 id="网站注册（最好使用google账号）"><a href="#网站注册（最好使用google账号）" class="headerlink" title="网站注册（最好使用google账号）"></a>网站注册（最好使用google账号）</h3><h3 id="仓库建立"><a href="#仓库建立" class="headerlink" title="仓库建立"></a>仓库建立</h3><p><img src="http://rg0quhtiy.hn-bkt.clouddn.com/hexoimg/202208041138948.png" alt="github2"></p><p><img src="http://rg0quhtiy.hn-bkt.clouddn.com/hexoimg/202208041138917.png" alt="github3"></p><p><img src="http://rg0quhtiy.hn-bkt.clouddn.com/hexoimg/202208041138155.png" alt="github4"></p><h3 id="配置git"><a href="#配置git" class="headerlink" title="配置git"></a>配置git</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">git</span> <span class="string">config</span> <span class="string">--global</span> <span class="string">user.name</span> <span class="string">"hwangkiki"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">git</span> <span class="string">config</span> <span class="string">--global</span> <span class="string">user.email</span> <span class="string">"hwangkiki.live@gmail.com"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>Tips: 代码最好是手动书写不然很容易报错，像这样。</p><p>打开blog文件夹（先获得文件夹的读/写权限）</p><h4 id="config-yml最下修改git"><a href="#config-yml最下修改git" class="headerlink" title="_config.yml最下修改git"></a>_config.yml最下修改git</h4><p>方法一：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">'git'</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/yourname/yourname.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">main</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>Tips: deploy: type: repo: branch: 后面都有一个英文的空格。</p><p>方法二：</p><p>使用vim命令，输入 i 进入编辑模式 </p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">vim_config.yml</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hwangkiki/picohub/img/%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2022-07-31%2016.44.59.png" alt="截屏2022-07-31 16.44.59"></p><p>修改完成后esc,  :wq 保存退出</p><h3 id="安装插件"><a href="#安装插件" class="headerlink" title="安装插件"></a>安装插件</h3><p>切换到blog目录下</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">npm</span> <span class="string">install</span> <span class="string">hexo-deployer-git</span> <span class="string">--save</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hwangkiki/picohub/img/%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2022-08-01%2014.56.24.png" alt="截屏2022-08-01 14.56.24"></p><p>三联套</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">clean</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">g</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">d</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h4 id="注意这里有个大坑搞了我整整一下午"><a href="#注意这里有个大坑搞了我整整一下午" class="headerlink" title="注意这里有个大坑搞了我整整一下午"></a>注意这里有个大坑搞了我整整一下午</h4><p><img src="http://rg0quhtiy.hn-bkt.clouddn.com/hexoimg/202208041140321.png" alt="hexod"></p><p>hexo d 推送到github仓库时，会显示输入github用户名和密码，输入用户名之后不要着急填写自己github的用户密码，因为github现在改变了认证的方式，要求使用token，密码由令牌代替。</p><p>settings&gt;Developer settings&gt;personal access tokens</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hwangkiki/picohub/img/%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2022-08-01%2015.11.51.png" alt="截屏2022-08-01 15.11.51"></p><p>获得密匙后就可以push了。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hwangkiki/picohub/img/%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2022-08-01%2015.01.30.png" alt="截屏2022-08-01 15.01.30"></p><p>就可以通过网址访问到自己的网站了</p><p><a href="https://yourname.github.io/">https://yourname.github.io/</a></p><p>安装主题,切换原始landscape主题</p><p>hexo 根目录下</p><p>方法一</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#git</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">git</span> <span class="string">clone</span> <span class="string">-b</span> <span class="string">master</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly.git</span> <span class="string">themes/butterfly</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>方法二</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#npm</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">npm</span> <span class="string">i</span> <span class="string">hexo-theme-butterfly</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>我自己的version”: “6.2.0” 用npm自动部署没有成功不知道为什么</p><p>如果你沒有 pug 以及 stylus 的渲染器</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">npm</span> <span class="string">install</span> <span class="string">hexo-renderer-pug</span> <span class="string">hexo-renderer-stylus</span> <span class="string">--save</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>先本地运行查看一下效果，然后再一套三连击，更新上传到github</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">clean</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">g</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">d</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>butterfly效果图</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hwangkiki/picohub/img/%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2022-08-01%2023.11.19.png" alt="截屏2022-08-01 23.11.19"></p><h5 id="截屏2022-08-01-23-11-35-x2F-Users-x2F-qihuang-x2F-Library-x2F-Application-Support-x2F-typora-user-images-x2F-截屏2022-08-01-23-11-35-png-试着写一篇博客"><a href="#截屏2022-08-01-23-11-35-x2F-Users-x2F-qihuang-x2F-Library-x2F-Application-Support-x2F-typora-user-images-x2F-截屏2022-08-01-23-11-35-png-试着写一篇博客" class="headerlink" title="![截屏2022-08-01 23.11.35](/Users/qihuang/Library/Application Support/typora-user-images/截屏2022-08-01 23.11.35.png)试着写一篇博客"></a>![截屏2022-08-01 23.11.35](/Users/qihuang/Library/Application Support/typora-user-images/截屏2022-08-01 23.11.35.png)试着写一篇博客</h5><p>切换到文件目录blog/source/_posts，一个.md文件</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">n</span> <span class="string">"我终于开始写文章了哈哈"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>_posts目录下就会出现相应的.md文件</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hwangkiki/picohub/img/%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2022-08-01%2022.45.26.png" alt="截屏2022-08-01 22.45.26"></p><p>Vim编辑器编辑文章（使用的markdown语法）</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">vim</span> <span class="string">我终于开始写文章了哈哈.md</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hwangkiki/picohub/img/%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2022-08-01%2023.06.03.png" alt="截屏2022-08-01 23.06.03"></p><p>修改完成后esc,  :wq 保存退</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hwangkiki/picohub/img/%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2022-08-01%2023.09.10-20220802104416918.png" alt="截屏2022-08-01 23.09.10"></p><p>OK，前期部署到这里就结束啦，关于hexo部署，butterfly主题美化大家可以看看这个up主的视频说得很详细</p><p>最后说一下部署期间需要用到的基本语法指令吧</p><p>hexo</p><table><thead><tr><th>hexo clean</th><th align="left">清除缓存</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>hexo g</td><td align="left">加载配置文件</td></tr><tr><td>hexo s</td><td align="left">启动hexo服务</td></tr><tr><td>hexo d</td><td align="left">推送本地数据</td></tr><tr><td>hexo n</td><td align="left">建立新文件、文件夹</td></tr><tr><td></td><td align="left"></td></tr></tbody></table><p>选定目录</p><table><thead><tr><th>cd</th><th>进入指定目录</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>cd ../</td><td>返回上层目录</td></tr><tr><td>cd ../..</td><td>返回上上层目录</td></tr></tbody></table><hr>]]></content>
      
      
      
